ricom — third-party asset notices
=================================

Fonts
-----
ricom bundles **no** font files or font-derived assets. On-screen text (the FPS
HUD, OSD toasts, `ricomctl notify`) is rendered at runtime from a TrueType font
supplied by the user via the `[font] path` setting in `ricom.toml`; glyphs are
rasterised on demand into an in-memory SDF glyph cache (see
`crates/backend-gl/src/text.rs`). No font is redistributed with ricom, so no
third-party font license applies to this repository.

If `[font] path` is empty or does not point at a usable `.ttf`, on-screen text is
simply disabled — the compositor still runs.
